 Midwestern United States]]\n[[Category:History of the Southern United States]]\n[[Category:Internal migrations in the United States]]\n[[Category:Northeastern United States]]\n[[Category:Western United States]]\n[[Category:20th century in the United States]]\n", "name_user": "2600:8807:a00:3b:78e4:5d80:a9:72c6", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eFirst migrations)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Great_Migration_(African_American)"}
