anding Book of a Musical\n| rowspan=\"2\" | Lin-Manuel Miranda\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Outstanding New Score\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Outstanding Director of a Musical\n| Thomas Kail\n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n| Outstanding Choreographer\n| Andy Blankenbuehler\n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Drama League Award]]s<ref>{{cite web |last=Gans |first=Andrew |url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/2015-drama-league-awards-nominations-announced-more-than-45-will-vie-for-distinguished-performance-honor-347266 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20150424013016/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/2015-drama-league-awards-nominations-announced-more-than-45-will-vie-for-distinguished-performance-honor-347266?r=n |archive-date=April 24, 2015 |title=2015 Drama League Awards Nominations Announced; More Than 45 Will Vie for Distinguished Performance Honor |work=Playbill |date=April 21, 2015 |accessdate=May 4, 2015 |url-status=dead |df=}}</ref>\n| colspan=\"2\" | Outstanding Production of a Broadway or Off-Broadway Musical\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | Distinguished Performance\n| Daveed Diggs\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Lin-Manuel Miranda\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"14\" | [[Drama Desk Award]]s<ref name=\"DDesk\">{{cite web |last=Gans |first=Andrew |url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/drama-desk-nominations-announced-hamilton-tops-the-list-347557 |title=Drama Desk Nominations Announced; ''Hamilton'' Tops the List |work=Playbill |date=April 23, 2015 |accessdate=May 4, 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150729171641/http://playbill.com/news/article/drama-desk-nominations-announced-hamilton-tops-the-list-347557 |archive-date=July 29, 2015}}</ref>\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Musical|Outstanding Musical]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Actor in a Musical|Outstanding Actor in a Musical]]\n| Lin-Manuel Miranda\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Featured Actor in a Musical|Outstanding Featured Actor in a Musical]]\n| Leslie Odom Jr.\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Featured Actress in a Musical|Outstanding Featured Actress in a Musical]]\n| Ren\u00e9e Elise Goldsberry\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Director of a Musical|Outstanding Director of a Musical]]\n| Thomas Kail\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Music|Outstanding Music]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" | Lin-Manuel Miranda\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Lyrics|Outstanding Lyrics]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Book of a Musical|Outstanding Book of a Musical]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Orchestrations|Outstanding Orchestrations]]\n| [[Alex Lacamoire]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Set Design|Outstanding Set Design]]\n| David Korins\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Costume Design|Outstanding Costume Design]]\n| Paul Tazewell\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Lighting Design|Outstanding Lighting Design]]\n| Howell Binkley\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Sound Design in a Musical|Outstanding Sound Design in a Musical]]\n| Nevin Steinberg\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Drama Desk Special Award|Special Award]] \u2021\n| Andy Blankenbuehler\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[New York Drama Critics' Circle#New York Drama Critics' Circle Award|New York Drama Critics' Circle Awards]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Hetrick |first=Adam |url=http://playbill.com/news/article/hamilton-and-between-riverside-and-crazy-win-2015-new-york-drama-critics-circle-awards-348317 |title=''Hamilton'' and ''Between Riverside and Crazy'' Win 2015 New York Drama Critics' Circle Awards |work=Playbill |date=May 4, 2015 |accessdate=May 4, 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150505021153/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/hamilton-and-between-riverside-and-crazy-win-2015-new-york-drama-critics-circle-awards-348317 |archivedate=May 5, 2015}}</ref>\n| colspan=\"2\" | Best Musical\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Off Broadway Alliance Awards<ref>{{cite web |author=BWW News Desk |url=http://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Off-Broadway-Alliance-Awards-Nominations-Announced-HAMILTON-INTO-THE-WOODS-CLINTON-BETWEEN-RIVERSIDE-CRAZY-More-20150506 |title=Off Broadway Alliance Awards Nominations Announced \u2013 ''HAMILTON'', ''INTO THE WOODS'', ''CLINTON'', ''BETWEEN RIVERSIDE & CRAZY'' & More... |website=BroadwayWorld.com |date=May 6, 2015 |accessdate=May 6, 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150508191917/http://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Off-Broadway-Alliance-Awards-Nominations-Announced-HAMILTON-INTO-THE-WOODS-CLINTON-BETWEEN-RIVERSIDE-CRAZY-More-20150506 |archivedate=May 8, 2015}}</ref>\n| colspan=\"2\" | Best New Musical\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Theatre World Award]]s<ref>{{cite web |last=Viagas |first=Robert |url=http://playbill.com/news/article/broadway-siblings-megan-and-robert-fairchild-among-71st-annual-theatre-world-award-winners-348368 |title=Broadway Siblings Megan and Robert Fairchild Among 71st Annual Theatre World Award Winners |work=Playbill |date=May 5, 2015 |accessdate=May 6, 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150507180643/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/broadway-siblings-megan-and-robert-fairchild-among-71st-annual-theatre-world-award-winners-348368 |archivedate=May 7, 2015}}</ref>\n| Outstanding Debut Performance\n| Daveed Diggs\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Clarence Derwent Awards]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Clement |first=Olivia |url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/phillipa-soo-and-josh-grisetti-named-most-promising-performers-by-actors-equity-348560 |title=Phillipa Soo and Josh Grisetti Named Most Promising Performers by Actors' Equity |work=Playbill |date=May 7, 2015 |accessdate=May 7, 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150508185138/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/phillipa-soo-and-josh-grisetti-named-most-promising-performers-by-actors-equity-348560