.com/article/Non-Stop-Alysha-Deslorieux-Taran-Killam-Anthony-Lee-Medina-and-More-Will-Join-Broadways-HAMILTON-This-Winter-20161214 |archivedate=December 15, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref> [[Brian d'Arcy James]] {{small|(April 18, 2017 \u2013 July 16, 2017)}};<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.theatermania.com/broadway/news/brian-darcy-james-hamilton-return-date_80320.html |title=It's Official! Brian d'Arcy James Sets Hamilton Return Date |last=Gordon |first=David |newspaper=TheaterMania.com |access-date=March 10, 2017 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312072703/http://www.theatermania.com/broadway/news/brian-darcy-james-hamilton-return-date_80320.html |archivedate=March 12, 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref> [[Euan Morton]] {{small|(July 28, 2017 \u2013 present)}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.playbill.com/article/euan-morton-is-hamiltons-next-king-george-on-broadway |title=Euan Morton Is Hamilton's Next King George on Broadway |website=Playbill |access-date=July 12, 2017}}</ref>\n* '''John Laurens / Philip Hamilton''' \u2013 [[Jordan Fisher]] {{small|(November 22, 2016 \u2013 March 5, 2017)}}<ref>{{cite web|author=BWW News Desk|url=http://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Recording-Artist-Jordan-Fisher-to-Make-Broadway-Debut-in-HAMILTON-Anthony-Ramos-to-Depart-Next-Month-20161019|title=Recording Artist Jordan Fisher to Make Broadway Debut in HAMILTON; Anthony Ramos to Depart Next Month|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020045642/http://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Recording-Artist-Jordan-Fisher-to-Make-Broadway-Debut-in-HAMILTON-Anthony-Ramos-to-Depart-Next-Month-20161019|archive-date=October 20, 2016|website=BroadwayWorld.com|date=October 19, 2016}}</ref>\n\n==== Chicago ====\n* '''Aaron Burr''' \u2013 [[Wayne Brady]];<ref>{{Cite news|date=Jan 9, 2017|url=http://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Its-Official-Wayne-Brady-Will-Play-Aaron-Burr-in-Chicagos-HAMILTON-20170109|title=It's Official! Wayne Brady Will Play 'Aaron Burr' in Chicago's HA